data.text:
I love seeing you guys out and about. Please let me know if you have any places and contacts that I can work with to keep this machine moving. Thanks again for supporting live music! SEE YOU SOON! richardsonacoustic@gmail.com

Its going to be a great Summer! I have a bunch of open Thursdays and Sunday if you know of anyplace wanting live music. Please let me know. richardsonacoustic@gmail.com

New songs are being updated in the live show catalog. Writing sessions and recordings are upcoming with hopes to get EP out in 2025.

http://app.mysetmusic.com/3551

It is my intent to promote positivity in this sometimes often negative environment. Let me know if you have an upcoming event that I can help with the music and entertainment. From backyard party to performing at Wimbley. I want to share the music and good times with you.
